For a list of the notifications a tab control can send to its parent window, see the **Notifications** section of [Tab Control Reference](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/windows/desktop/bb760548) in the [!INCLUDE[winSDK](../atl/includes/winsdk_md.md)].  \n  \n## See Also  \n [Using CTabCtrl](../mfc/using-ctabctrl.md)   \n [Controls](../mfc/controls-mfc.md)\n\n"}